  "remarks": "TAi.066 Title: Mullah. Designation: a) Mayor of Kandahar under the Taliban regime, b) Minister of Public Health under the Taliban regime. Member of Taliban Supreme Council in charge of the Medical Committee as of Jan. 2011. Directly supervises three medical centers caring for wounded Taliban fighters as of mid-2013. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Barakzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
